&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Stay up to date with competitor offerings, where BitMEX stands in terms of product suite, volumes, market share; proactively identify areas we should be focusing on.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
