&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborating with the rest of the DevOps teams to include dashboards/alerts as a standard in our self-service applications (e.g. database-as-a-service)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
