&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Trading Engine sits at the core of the BitMEX platform and handles all brokerage and trading aspects. The Trading Engine team is responsible for order management, risk checking, position keeping, PNL calculations, derivatives pricing, risk management, market data distribution, order matching, and settlement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are building a best-in-class engineering team to help us scale the BitMEX trading platform to millions of users and millions of transactions per second. We are looking for experts in electronic trading system development, microservice architecture, and scaling, who is also knowledgeable of the business logic.&lt;/p&gt;
